<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10"><div class="flex justify-between"><h1 class="text-3xl font-black">تقرير المخزون والتسوية</h1><%= render "admin/reports/export" %></div><%= render "admin/reports/filters" %><div class="mt-7 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-5"><% @report.cards.each do |name, value| %><div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-5"><span class="text-sm text-slate-500"><%= name %></span><strong class="block text-2xl"><%= value %></strong></div><% end %></div><section class="mt-7 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-5"><h2 class="text-xl font-black">فحوص السلامة</h2><dl class="mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2"><% @report.warnings.each do |name, count| %><div class="flex justify-between rounded-xl bg-white p-3"><dt><%= name %></dt><dd class="font-black"><%= count %></dd></div><% end %></dl><p class="mt-3 text-sm">هذه قائمة تشخيصية ولا تنفذ إصلاحات تلقائية.</p></section></div>
